<div class="hero-unit">
<p>
<h3>The Get-to-know-you site</h3>
<img src="images/brain.jpg"/>
<h5>
  Pictures are great for capturing memories and sharing ideas, but they are not great for knowing a person. On social and dating sites, we often judge people based on their picture, and someone-else's creativity which they endorse. Their humorous, witty or thought provoking comments lose importance among the flashy snaps and clips. This site will guide you present yourself to the world without pictures. Browse a profile and you will know. 
